Package cloudsim.ext

Interface Summary
Constants  
GeoLocatable Interface GeoLocatable should be implemented by any simulation entity that can be physically located within a region of the Simulation World.
 

Class Summary
Internet The class Internet emulates the function of the real world Internet.
InternetCharacteristics This class holds the data that define the behaviour of the Internet which includes latencies and bandwidth, and also provides methods to access those information.
InternetCloudlet This class which extends Cloudlet acts as a container for requests and responses exchanged between UserBases and DatacenterControllers.
Simulation Main controller class of the simulation.
UserBase A User Base models a group of users that is considered as a single unit in the simulation and its main responsibility is to generate traffic for the simulation.
